Description:
Contains the runtime APIs that allow SceneCore to work on multiple devices. Developers are not expected to interact directly with these APIs, but rather use the ones from the top-level SceneCore library.

See also: https://developer.android.com/jetpack/androidx/releases/xr-scenecore#1.0.0-alpha08


